    "This processed dataset contains 7,761 locomotive maintenance records.",
    "The dataset has been divided into training, validation, and test sets, following a ratio of 6:2:2.",
    "Additionally, Jieba was employed as the Chinese segmentation tool throughout the experimental process.",
    "Hyperparameters The settings of the hyperparameters of the experiments in this section are shown in Table 5, and these settings include the number of batches, number of GPUs, learning rate, number of threads, maximum input length and maximum output length.",
    "Metrics In this paper, Bleu-4, Rouge-1, Rouge-2 and Rouge-L are used as evaluation metrics."
